{"tid":2327464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 昨獲〈Panorama〉首冠　「謝謝 WIZ*ONE 為我們加油！」","createTime":"2020-12-16T05:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T07:26:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1debc1d2357dcf604eea44a7a8fab468638113ad","tid":2327464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b256352d67b34e0fde5800c4c8c890dd/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-15/132351-889085.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b256352d67b34e0fde5800c4c8c890dd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-15%2F132351-889085.png&h=9e9160cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIZ*ONE 今年已三度發片，每次都帶來令人驚艷的作品，而昨晚她們也在回歸後首度征服音樂節目。恭喜 IZ*ONE！<br />\n<br />\n昨天（15 日）在 SBS MTV 播出的《The Show》中，IZ*ONE 憑著最新主打歌 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 擊敗了 ENHYPEN 和 MOMOLAND，成為 12 月第三週的冠軍得主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f016715e9624bcfb7185ccbbca5f2a48/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-15/132351-889086.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f016715e9624bcfb7185ccbbca5f2a48%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-15%2F132351-889086.jpg&h=1f4b8499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 獲獎後表示：「這是我們第一次用 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 這首歌得獎，很感謝和我們一起辛苦準備的公司同仁。」IZ*ONE 說道：「聽說今天的節目是今年最後一集《The Show》，很榮幸我們 IZ*ONE 能參與，希望大家在年底都健健康康的，也謝謝 WIZ*ONE 為我們加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c1808d2b01741bceae3d25b6074b13db/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-15/132351-889087.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c1808d2b01741bceae3d25b6074b13db%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-15%2F132351-889087.jpeg&h=81c134e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再度恭喜 IZ*ONE！最後就來重溫她們昨天的表演和安可吧～"},{"pid":"9e0d3163ed8f8aa9ec30217969da8d69038f6388","tid":2327464,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"支持！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875f3d59ed4bc9e16d7ae472f9d94a1b28c9f964","tid":2327464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e0d3163ed8f8aa9ec30217969da8d69038f6388","tid":2327464,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"支持！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"太勁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd46499eb30e297aebdaf39fd5ed5b2fb3bc4c4","tid":2327464,"uid":205928,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"永續IZONE !!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/16/133956_739ea0e010cffb49550257d94ca63a16.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F133956_739ea0e010cffb49550257d94ca63a16.gif&h=730dbc40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34f1ae7cd7ee22a439cfe9775bdf242038f7b03","tid":2327464,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"875f3d59ed4bc9e16d7ae472f9d94a1b28c9f964","tid":2327464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e0d3163ed8f8aa9ec30217969da8d69038f6388","tid":2327464,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"支持！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"太勁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"腸是Wizone來的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca745797065bc30c3d4a5f21aef1046d4c57c047","tid":2327464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b34f1ae7cd7ee22a439cfe9775bdf242038f7b03","tid":2327464,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi